                                </layout>
                            </layoutDesc>
                        </objectDesc>

                        <handDesc>
                            <handNote scope="sole" xml:id="hand-1">
                                <p>The text was copied in a <term type="script">mixed minuscule
                                        Perlschrift</term> with variable slant, in brown ink, with
                                    minimal variation in letter size.</p>
                                <p>Syllabic abbreviations are not used, apart from the horizontal
                                    stroke for <hi rend="italic">nu</hi>, which appears only at the
                                    end of lines, while superscript word endings do not appear,
                                    although suspensions of word endings are present. Breathings are
                                    both angular and round, and mute <hi rend="italic">iota</hi> is
                                    absent. Use of the double dot is functional only, and <foreign xml:lang="la">nomina sacra</foreign> are unaccentuated. The
                                    double grave accent is in use.</p>
                                <p>Punctuation used includes the middle and upper points, lower and
                                    middle commas, question mark and full stop.</p>
                            </handNote>
                        </handDesc>

                        <decoDesc>
